{"tid":1728141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位連登醫師，有事一問","createTime":"2019-11-16T17:46:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T19:51:20.000Z","uid":143774,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd50057857253afcf9207af4208784de5085275","tid":1728141,"uid":143774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:46:50.000Z","msg":"小弟係廚師嚟，最近天氣凍返啲，好多客叫避風塘炒蟹，加上我成日都第一個開爐，所以成日整，啲辣椒原本用開英國貨，後尾無哂貨之後又翻中國貨，最近英國翻咗貨，唔知係咪吸得多辣椒，想問會唔會灼傷咽喉位？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mq3cZ9N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fmq3cZ9N.jpg&h=b3c94ab1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最近都會隱隱地痛，早排好似有燒傷嘅感覺咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係喉嚨痛個位上少少？<br />\n<br />\n係咪已經可以退出廚師界，要休養幾耐先有得再出嚟煮野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多唔多廚師有呢個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我熱愛我自己啲工作架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dc6f7c3726075cdba8816205c896b20e514dcf","tid":1728141,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:48:46.000Z","msg":"政府打緊公關戰同輿論戰，口誅筆伐黎解散呢場運動，手足知唔知我地下一步要點做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728096</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"153939d3120c81375c11df768ecf19760dc5abae","tid":1728141,"uid":305964,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T17:50:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87d4058fa2a4775a546df74ef8502a9f63ba4d28","tid":1728141,"uid":40054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:00:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ac6e9e6a931f3af200b7ea67933384777079747a","tid":1728141,"uid":237487,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:02:29.000Z","msg":"Tg ask 國難忠醫好嗎"},{"pid":"1ba46816f7086644cf48a47cf13bff0691ca02c5","tid":1728141,"uid":117276,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"